\u30b5\u30f3\u30c0\u30f3\u30b9\u6620\u753b\u796d\u3067\u306e\u4e0a\u6620\uff082019\u5e74\uff09\u3001\u30a2\u30cc\u30b7\u30fc\u56fd\u969b\u30a2\u30cb\u30e1\u30fc\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u6620\u753b\u796d\u300c\u30d9\u30b9\u30c8VR\u4f53\u9a13\u8cde\u300d\u53d7\u8cde\uff082019\u5e74\uff09\u3001SXSW\u300c\u5be9\u67fb\u54e1\u8cde\uff08\u30b9\u30c8\u30fc\u30ea\u30fc\u90e8\u9580\uff09\u300d\u53d7\u8cde\uff082019\u5e74\uff09\u3002\n\n\u5236\u4f5c\u306fJorge Tereso\u3068Fernando Maldonado\u3002\u88fd\u4f5c\uff1aAtlas V\u3001Oculus\u3001Arte France\u3001Ryot, Albyon\u30011STAveMachine\u3002\u5354\u8cdb\uff1aKaleidoscope\u3001Rh\u00f4ne Alpes Cin\u00e9ma\u3001Youtube\u3001CNC\u3002 \n", "short_description": "\u30b3\u30ea\u30f3\u30fb\u30d5\u30a1\u30ec\u30eb\u306e\u58f0\u3067\u8d08\u308b\u300eGloomy Eyes\u300f\u306f\u3001\u4eba\u9593\u306b\u611b\u60f3\u3092\u5c3d\u304b\u3057\u305f\u592a\u967d\u304c\u96a0\u308c\u3066\u3057\u307e\u3044\u3001\u6607\u3089\u306a\u304f\u306a\u3063\u3066\u3057\u307e\u3046\u7269\u8a9e\u30026DoF&\u30ea\u30a2\u30eb\u30bf\u30a4\u30e03D\u306eVR\u30a2\u30cb\u30e1\u30b7\u30ea\u30fc\u30ba\u3067\u3059\u3002\n"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "313099916508429", "locale": "es_ES", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Gloomy Eyes", "keywords": ["Tiny", "Zombie", "Movie", "Narrative", "Animation"], "long_description": "En un mundo plenamente oscuro, Gloomy, un ni\u00f1o zombi se enamora de Nina, una ni\u00f1a humana. Su amor buscar\u00e1 trascender los l\u00edmites de un mundo en el que vivos y muertos son incapaces de coexistir en armon\u00eda.\n\nGLOOMY EYES es una serie de animaci\u00f3n en realidad virtual, a 6 grados de libertad, en 3D y lanzada como trilog\u00eda. Narrada por Jorge Drexel.\n\nEstrenada en el Festival de Cine de Sundance (2019), galardonada con la \"Mejor experiencia de realidad virtual\" en en Festival Internacional de Cine de Animaci\u00f3n de Annecy (2019) y ganadora del \"Premio del Jurado a Mejor \u2018Storytelling\u2019\" en SXSW (2019).\n", "short_description": "En un mundo plenamente oscuro, Gloomy, un ni\u00f1o zombi se enamora de Nina, una ni\u00f1a humana. Su amor buscar\u00e1 trascender los l\u00edmites de un mundo en el que vivos y muertos son incapaces de coexistir en armon\u00eda."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "2746845142029907", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974628_189869579098187_1385099778701918208_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=u-vHQkBGTSkQ7kNvgHH9NBi&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDpGjolmT19S7D3NeCge5klrBKfYCfrKnu0V8F4xSV_yA&oe=673B39F1"}, {"file_name": "01w5jV.png", "id": "2732668053508327", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982699_2732668056841660_2501815409083154432_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=BpMMQUHNmoUQ7kNvgHpGflF&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDtfaZxiipIAouvekyaycvBdvR60-_8gV8E2-JVCDfxjA&oe=673B2904"}, {"file_name": "RqxmKN.png", "id": "1080093842386804", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984441_1080093845720137_1783910835282771968_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=cTMwk-upsh8Q7kNvgE8Y5z-&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAeCqwBeMAv1-fP7RBwXL-pPFTCPa9od_J0bjVozIE6yg&oe=673B3FB2"}, {"file_name": "QX3Tth.png", "id": "936140620155889", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974452_936140623489222_5127119442982993920_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=llByDSyuUHoQ7kNvgETAgSO&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDgLjeR3rH8lbc1ajuLsTwuWy0sFCWUGGcVJ-8vmL_Thw&oe=673B41D1"}, {"file_name": "migrated_image.png", "id": "641598973285699", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.